<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[باب الغين والزاي]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[الغين والزاي والدال]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">غزد:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الغِزْيَدُ:</span> الشَّديدُ الصَّوْتِ. والناعِمُ من النَّبات.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">زغد:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">الزَّغْدُ:</span> الهَدِيْرُ الشَّدِيدُ. وتَزَغُّدُ الشِّقْشِقَةِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">والزَّغْدُ:</span> مَلْءُ الإِناءِ والسِّقَاء.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">والإِزْغَادُ:</span> الإِرْضاع.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">والمُزْغَئدُّ:</span> من النَّعْمَة.<span class="c5"> وعاشَ عَيْشاً زَغْداً:</span> أي رَغْداً.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وفلانٌ مُزْغَئدُّ:</span> أي غَضْبان.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وزَغَدَ فلانٌ صاحِبَه بالكلام:</span> أي حَرَّشَه.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">والزَّغّادُ:</span> المُصَوِّتُ <span class="c2">(١)</span> الذي كأنَّه مَخْنُوقٌ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">زدغ:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">المِزْدَغَةُ:</span> لُغَةٌ في المِصْدَغَة، وتَزَدَّغْتُ به <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في ك: والزغاد المصوب.<br>(٢) كذا في الأصول، وفي العباب والقاموس: بها.</p> </div>